Hail, Hail, Uncle Ho,<br>
He kicked the shit out of G.I.Joe.<br><br>
Not one word, nor text book can change that fact.<br>
The war is Viet Nam was lost; American chose not to act.<br><br>
The USA did not nuke them into a parking lot,<br>
It just left them as what it was, a fucking flop.<br><br>
So to Ed, Injun Chief, and Art, warrier with a mop,<br>
and Cook, flag waving soldier of mighty flame,<br>
take this from a voice that has no name, no fame,<br>
stick this in your pipe and pull a mighty toke,<br>
cause like the war, you all are a joke.<br><br>
I got no name, I got no address,<br>
I got no cause, I got no shit to dress,<br>
I am just tired of you bullshit grunts.<br>
and that doc spatz, he can go hump,<br><br>
Let it go, it's all done.  F*** the rest of you!<br><br>

